description: This is the ultimate no-fuss summer dinner. Cook chicken kebabs, pair with a pre-made Asian salad kit and devour in a soft bread rolls.
keywords: Chicken sandwich,Quick & easy dinner,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Seafood free,BBQ chicken,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Chicken
name: Honey Soy Chicken Rolls With Sriracha Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 375g Woolworths COOK honey soy chicken kebabs

recipeInstructions.text: Heat a greased barbecue plate or chargrill over medium-low heat. Cook kebabs for 15 minutes, turning occasionally, or until cooked through. Remove chicken from skewers.
Meanwhile, make salad kit according to packet instructions.
Using a small knife, cut roll tops down the centre, ensuring not to cut all the way through. Fill rolls with salad, chicken, onion and coriander. Drizzle with sriracha sauce and serve.
